headline.main: No. 13 Duke Beats No. 16 Miami 57-52 to Get to ACC Finals
headline.print_headline: No. 13 Duke Beats No. 16 Miami 57-52 to Get to ACC Finals

lead_paragraph: With the game on the line, Lexie Brown made the key plays down the stretch and Duke got the defensive stops it needed to get back to the ACC Tournament final for the first time in a few years.
